1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:02,070
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,070 --> 00:00:03,710
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,710 --> 00:00:05,110
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,380 --> 00:00:09,210
Chairman Park isn't
the forgiving type.

5
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:11,080
Not at all.

6
00:00:17,760 --> 00:00:20,860
It's me.
Where are you meeting Chairman Park?

7
00:00:21,190 --> 00:00:23,860
What's it to you? Our deal is over.

8
00:00:24,860 --> 00:00:28,130
So what if our deal is over?
I can still give you advice.

9
00:00:29,230 --> 00:00:33,070
You're not meeting Chairman Park
without a plan, are you?

10
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:37,540
Tell me where,
just in case something happens.

11
00:00:39,010 --> 00:00:42,250
James,
get to the Adele warehouse now.

12
00:00:42,710 --> 00:00:44,180
I'll explain when I see you.

13
00:00:54,090 --> 00:00:55,690
(Incoming Call)

14
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:02,100
(Incoming Call)

15
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,040
Watch out!

16
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:41,640
You crossed the line today.

17
00:01:43,540 --> 00:01:45,640
You're the one who crossed it first.

18
00:01:46,580 --> 00:01:49,350
Even though I warned you
that I knew about Munhwadang,

19
00:01:50,180 --> 00:01:53,050
you still framed Min Jun
and put him in danger.

20
00:01:54,420 --> 00:01:55,620
That's enough, both of you.

21
00:01:56,650 --> 00:02:00,120
It looks like both Hyun Jun
and Min Jun have been hurt enough.

22
00:02:01,660 --> 00:02:02,660
This is where it ends.

23
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,230
No.

24
00:02:05,130 --> 00:02:07,070
My Hyun Jun is the only one
who got hurt.

25
00:02:08,570 --> 00:02:10,170
No matter what it takes,

26
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,770
I'll make you pay
for what you did to him.

27
00:02:15,910 --> 00:02:16,910
Just you wait.

28
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,790
She killed someone?

29
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:41,070
She raised me
with hands that killed someone?

30
00:02:44,970 --> 00:02:46,200
My own mother...

31
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:50,280
How could my own mother
do such a thing?

32
00:02:53,850 --> 00:02:54,850
What if...

33
00:02:57,050 --> 00:02:58,820
What if what happened
seven years ago is true?

34
00:03:01,950 --> 00:03:05,390
If all these rumors are true,
then...

35
00:03:09,260 --> 00:03:10,430
What does that make me?

36
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:15,000
Damn it!

37
00:03:27,010 --> 00:03:30,250
I heard some of the shareholders
are making a fuss...

38
00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:32,550
over the rumors about my wife.

39
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:36,350
Were you behind this?

40
00:03:37,290 --> 00:03:38,290
Me?

41
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,120
Last time, you definitely...

42
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:43,260
kept digging
into the Munhwadang affair.

43
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,830
I bet you made use...

44
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:49,430
of what you found out back then.

45
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:53,040
Yes, you're right, sir.

46
00:03:53,970 --> 00:03:57,510
I asked you about Munhwadang
after hearing the rumor.

47
00:03:58,740 --> 00:04:00,780
But that's as far as it went.

48
00:04:01,410 --> 00:04:03,510
I just dismissed it as a rumor.

49
00:04:05,050 --> 00:04:07,890
So you have nothing to do
with what happened today?

50
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:12,460
Rumors have a way of spreading,
don't they?

51
00:04:13,730 --> 00:04:16,160
Someone who heard
the same rumor I did...

52
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,960
must be one of Adele's shareholders.

53
00:04:23,370 --> 00:04:26,470
I'm pretty sure I warned you.

54
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:30,840
I told you
not to take your schemes too far.

55
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:35,010
I can tolerate
you going after my wife,

56
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:38,080
but I draw the line
at you destabilizing Adele.

57
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:42,150
You'd be wise to stop here.

58
00:04:43,490 --> 00:04:45,390
If the damage gets out of control,

59
00:04:46,290 --> 00:04:48,060
I won't be able to let it slide.

60
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,190
Damage control?

61
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:53,500
Is he planning to make this
all go away quickly?

62
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:57,270
Why aren't you answering?

63
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:03,070
Since I'm not the one who did it,
I'm not sure how to answer.

64
00:05:09,010 --> 00:05:12,050
Sir, I have something urgent
to report.

65
00:05:14,890 --> 00:05:15,890
You may go.

66
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:17,960
Yes, sir.

67
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,630
Of course Chairman Park
suspects you.

68
00:05:29,370 --> 00:05:32,470
It's a direct attack on Oh Jung Ran,
so of course he'd blame us for it.

69
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:34,670
That's why
he's underestimating the situation.

70
00:05:36,310 --> 00:05:38,480
He thinks he can just
threaten me a little...

71
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:40,810
and then dismiss all this
as a baseless rumor.

72
00:05:41,910 --> 00:05:45,320
But I'll keep fanning the flames
of this rumor.

73
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,950
Until the demands
for Hyun Jun's dismissal...

74
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:50,020
become impossible to ignore.

75
00:05:50,350 --> 00:05:54,660
You're right. For Min Jun's sake,
we have to remove Park Hyun Jun.

76
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:59,400
I know Min Jun is still more worried
about Hyun Jun's feelings,

77
00:05:59,930 --> 00:06:01,630
but I have to put Min Jun first.

78
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:05,400
I can't afford to hesitate or waver.

79
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:10,640
What do you mean you failed?

80
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:13,310
Are you telling me
Choi Yu Na is still alive?

81
00:06:13,710 --> 00:06:14,710
I'm sorry, sir.

82
00:06:15,410 --> 00:06:17,450
Chloe showed up at the scene.

83
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,120
Why was she there?

84
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:21,220
We haven't been able
to determine that yet.

85
00:06:21,550 --> 00:06:24,720
She was injured saving Choi Yu Na,
and they were taken to the hospital.

86
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:27,560
She said she'd stay out
of the deal with Choi Yu Na,

87
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:30,730
and now she's stepping in again
and ruining my plans?

88
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:34,600
So, what condition are they in?

89
00:06:36,130 --> 00:06:38,800
Jin Ju was in an accident.
She's in the hospital.

90
00:06:50,110 --> 00:06:51,120
Hey.

91
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,250
Are you awake?

92
00:06:59,460 --> 00:07:00,730
How's Choi Yu Na?

93
00:07:00,990 --> 00:07:01,990
Right.

94
00:07:02,490 --> 00:07:05,530
She suffered a minor head injury
in the accident,

95
00:07:05,730 --> 00:07:06,800
but she's all right.

96
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:13,540
That's a relief.

97
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,040
What on earth happened?

98
00:07:17,610 --> 00:07:21,380
Choi Yu Na seemed to think
Chairman Park had forgiven her.

99
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:26,120
But from what I saw,
he looked ready to kill her.

100
00:07:27,790 --> 00:07:31,220
Him asking her to meet
set off alarm bells in my head.

101
00:07:34,330 --> 00:07:37,060
You said you'd have Park Tae Ho
and Choi Yu Na kill each other.

102
00:07:37,900 --> 00:07:41,000
But when the moment of truth came,
you changed your mind, didn't you?

103
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:43,070
That's why you saved Choi Yu Na.

104
00:07:43,430 --> 00:07:47,440
I didn't save Choi Yu Na.
I just got in Park Tae Ho's way.

105
00:07:48,170 --> 00:07:49,170
In his way?

106
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:53,680
Park Tae Ho would kill Choi Yu Na
and cover it up without a trace.

107
00:07:54,850 --> 00:07:58,080
Once again, he would've benefited
from Adele's money...

108
00:07:58,450 --> 00:07:59,650
and power.

109
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,150
If that happened,

110
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:05,060
there'd be only
one option left for me.

111
00:08:06,660 --> 00:08:09,860
Killing Park Tae Ho
with my own hands.

112
00:08:10,930 --> 00:08:12,200
Jin Ju, please.

113
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:18,300
Isn't it better to save Choi Yu Na
and use her as a pawn?

114
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:24,110
Park Tae Ho doesn't deserve the law.
He deserves to die.

115
00:08:25,210 --> 00:08:29,010
And Choi Yu Na must become a killer
and have her life ruined.

116
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,520
I didn't do it for Choi Yu Na.

117
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:35,020
I did it for my revenge,

118
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,660
for the ending I want.

119
00:08:38,590 --> 00:08:39,760
That's why I put my life
on the line.

120
00:08:49,070 --> 00:08:51,500
Right. I'm the one who called him.

121
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,740
Something happened to you,

122
00:08:54,370 --> 00:08:55,510
and I thought he should know.

123
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,890
You should go.

124
00:09:16,230 --> 00:09:18,330
- I'm not even hurt that badly.
- Was that...

125
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,830
your plan?

126
00:09:27,570 --> 00:09:29,340
I heard everything
from outside your room.

127
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:33,010
Using Choi Yu Na to kill my father.

128
00:09:34,310 --> 00:09:35,950
Is that the revenge you want?

129
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:49,590
Never mind Choi Yu Na.
It's Chloe that worries me.

130
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:52,300
She keeps getting in my way.

131
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:55,530
Send someone to the hospital.
I want eyes on both of them.

132
00:09:56,030 --> 00:10:00,300
Depending on what happens,
I may need the job finished.

133
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:02,370
Someone to finish the job?

134
00:10:04,210 --> 00:10:05,240
Where's...

135
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:08,580
Oh Jung Ran right now?

136
00:10:19,220 --> 00:10:20,620
Why are you so tense?

137
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:25,530
It makes the rumor
that you're a murderer seem...

138
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:27,930
even more believable.

139
00:10:28,430 --> 00:10:29,430
Hon...

140
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:31,240
Honey.

141
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:36,940
Did you really kill
the woman you served?

142
00:10:38,140 --> 00:10:39,610
Did you drug...

143
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:42,380
the lady of Munhwadang and kill her?

144
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:47,520
Wait. Are you asking
because you really don't know?

145
00:10:49,020 --> 00:10:51,120
You suspected it all along,
didn't you?

146
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,600
I did.

147
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:08,040
I figured you'd need to be that capable
to be useful.

148
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:09,510
What?

149
00:11:10,070 --> 00:11:11,810
Useful?

150
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:16,180
Not everyone can take a human life,
you know.

151
00:11:16,450 --> 00:11:20,050
Only someone that capable
could handle the tasks...

152
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:22,520
I give you.

153
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:25,260
That's why I made you the madam...

154
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,660
of this house.

155
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:29,390
So you knew all along.

156
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:33,500
Then a stupid rumor like this
shouldn't matter.

157
00:11:33,930 --> 00:11:35,230
Wrong.

158
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:39,870
It's a different story
if the public finds out.

159
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:44,640
The madam of Adele is a murderer?

160
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:49,250
Even as a rumor,
it's driving our stock price down.

161
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:51,180
So, take care of it.

162
00:11:51,450 --> 00:11:54,190
And do it quickly,
before Hyun Jun's name is ruined.

163
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:58,220
For your son. No, for Adele.

164
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:01,730
You can easily make
this rumor disappear, can't you?

165
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,390
We'll see.

166
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:08,670
I'll have to decide
which would be more effective.

167
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:15,170
Silencing the rumor
or getting rid of you.

168
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:21,080
Honey, I can still be useful.
I'll do anything.

169
00:12:22,550 --> 00:12:23,550
Anything?

170
00:12:24,650 --> 00:12:28,220
You'll do anything I tell you to do?

171
00:12:30,250 --> 00:12:32,420
Why are you testing me
all of a sudden?

172
00:12:32,860 --> 00:12:35,790
I've done everything
you've ever asked of me.

173
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,700
In exchange for making
this rumor go away,

174
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:40,660
what is it you want me to do?

175
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:44,670
We need to deal with this quickly
for Hyun Jun's sake,

176
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:47,540
so stop beating around the bush
and tell me what you want.

177
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:54,110
Right. Excellent.

178
00:12:55,110 --> 00:12:59,380
This is the Oh Jung Ran
I know and like.

179
00:13:31,950 --> 00:13:33,850
- Watch your step.
- Goodness.

180
00:13:34,220 --> 00:13:35,620
- Goodness.
- My gosh.

181
00:13:35,690 --> 00:13:38,060
- Gosh, my back.
- Oh dear.

182
00:13:38,660 --> 00:13:40,760
- This is awful.
- My gosh.

183
00:13:41,660 --> 00:13:42,790
For goodness' sake.

184
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:46,900
My goodness.
How is it still this bad?

185
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,900
They said the acupuncturist
worked miracles.

186
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:50,470
Miracle worker, my foot.

187
00:13:50,770 --> 00:13:53,800
I'm telling you,
Western medicine is better for me.

188
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:56,940
How many times do I have to say
I'd rather get an IV drip?

189
00:13:57,410 --> 00:14:01,250
Your mouth seems to be working fine,
so I guess it's finally kicking in.

190
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:03,980
Now shut your trap
and drink your herbal medicine.

191
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:08,790
How can I drink with my trap shut?
I have to open it to drink.

192
00:14:08,990 --> 00:14:10,820
For goodness' sake.

193
00:14:11,220 --> 00:14:13,120
I notice you're not saying
you won't drink it.

194
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:15,960
You're a sucker
for anything healthy.

195
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,990
It's not like...

196
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:19,300
I want to drink it.

197
00:14:19,830 --> 00:14:21,230
It'd be a waste not to.

198
00:14:21,430 --> 00:14:23,970
For crying out loud. What?

199
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:30,040
I'm getting a call.
Hold on, let me check.

200
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:36,280
Who is it?

201
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:39,480
Who's this? It's an unknown number.

202
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:40,990
Don't pick up
if you don't know who it is.

203
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,820
Voice phishing scams
are rampant these days.

204
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,420
Voice phishing?

205
00:14:45,990 --> 00:14:47,490
My goodness,
the nerve of those people!

206
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:50,830
Come on. That's why
I'm telling you not to answer.

207
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:52,800
You'll just end up cussing them out.

208
00:14:54,230 --> 00:14:56,100
The phone stopped ringing.

209
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:57,400
Hold on.

210
00:14:58,740 --> 00:15:02,040
Has Yu Na gone out? It's so quiet.

211
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,440
I know, right?

212
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,480
We tried reaching
the patient's emergency contact,

213
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,510
but couldn't get through.

214
00:15:09,010 --> 00:15:10,050
Is that so?

215
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:13,150
I can fill out any urgent paperwork.

216
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:16,290
Then please come to the front desk.
There are a few forms to fill out.

217
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:18,160
Sure. Of course.

218
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,470
It should end here.

219
00:15:34,470 --> 00:15:35,840
And then what?

220
00:15:36,310 --> 00:15:39,310
If you want revenge,
find another way.

221
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:44,780
Seven years ago,

222
00:15:46,050 --> 00:15:47,080
after suffering so much,

223
00:15:48,420 --> 00:15:50,790
this was the only option I saw.

224
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:56,430
This is the ending I've spent
the last seven years hoping for,

225
00:15:57,460 --> 00:15:58,800
and no one...

226
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:02,130
has the right to tell me to give up.

227
00:16:02,670 --> 00:16:04,100
No one...

228
00:16:05,070 --> 00:16:06,340
can understand...

229
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:08,370
the pain I've endured...

230
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:11,380
or the rage inside me!

231
00:16:13,210 --> 00:16:15,550
You know this isn't the right way.

232
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:36,170
My dad...

233
00:16:37,940 --> 00:16:40,270
I left him trapped in those flames,

234
00:16:41,540 --> 00:16:44,510
and I couldn't do a thing.

235
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,240
Every time I close my eyes,

236
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:51,550
I relive that moment.
It's a nightmare every single day!

237
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:56,420
The guilt of being the only survivor
made me want to die.

238
00:16:58,060 --> 00:17:02,630
My father is dead,
and I feel like I'm dying,

239
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:06,000
but Park Tae Ho and Choi Yu Na
get to eat,

240
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,930
sleep, laugh, and live their lives.

241
00:17:09,430 --> 00:17:11,100
How's that fair?

242
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:14,710
What's wrong
with wanting to set that straight?

243
00:17:16,410 --> 00:17:19,110
Why shouldn't I be allowed...

244
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:22,450
to kill the people
who murdered my father?

245
00:17:36,530 --> 00:17:37,660
See?

246
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:40,260
You really are...

247
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:43,070
your father's son, after all.

248
00:17:44,470 --> 00:17:49,140
You say you can't forgive your dad
and that you'll help me,

249
00:17:49,210 --> 00:17:53,080
but when I say I'll kill your dad,
you're the first to object.

250
00:17:55,010 --> 00:17:58,120
I don't care what you say.

251
00:17:58,650 --> 00:18:00,450
I'll see this through to the end.

252
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:02,090
I swear...

253
00:18:02,150 --> 00:18:03,720
I will kill your father...

254
00:18:07,420 --> 00:18:08,930
This isn't about my father.

255
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:13,230
I'm doing this for you, not him.
Jin Ju, you're not a killer!

256
00:18:15,670 --> 00:18:17,530
You couldn't kill someone...

257
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:20,770
and keep living
as though nothing happened.

258
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:24,240
That's why I'm doing this.

259
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:27,850
I'm afraid you'll be destroyed,
that you'll shatter!

260
00:18:29,980 --> 00:18:31,720
Even now, all I want...

261
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:36,950
is to protect you.

262
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:15,890
What is this?
What are you trying to do to me?

263
00:19:17,730 --> 00:19:19,160
You're such a pain.

264
00:19:20,030 --> 00:19:21,630
I wanted to handle this quietly.

265
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:23,970
Handle this?

266
00:19:24,740 --> 00:19:25,740
Don't tell me...

267
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:35,110
Did the chairman send you?
Are you really here to kill me?

268
00:19:35,850 --> 00:19:38,980
Why else do you think I'm here?

269
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:42,320
You're the one who started this
with your threats and blackmail.

270
00:19:42,890 --> 00:19:45,520
Don't blame me.
This is what happens...

271
00:19:45,620 --> 00:19:47,860
when you overplay your hand.

272
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:50,560
No. I was just...

273
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:52,230
Chloe.

274
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:53,960
What?

275
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:56,000
Chloe was the one who made me do it.

276
00:19:57,940 --> 00:20:01,240
Right.
This is my only way out of this.

277
00:20:03,740 --> 00:20:07,840
I'm not the one
the chairman should kill. Chloe is.

278
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:09,650
Chloe?

279
00:20:17,790 --> 00:20:20,590
Please, don't do this.
Just end it here.

280
00:20:24,830 --> 00:20:26,030
This is my business.

281
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,430
Don't talk like you know anything
about it.

282
00:20:28,900 --> 00:20:32,600
Okay, I get it.
Just go inside and get some rest.

283
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:35,270
You're still recovering.

284
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:37,980
You shouldn't be pushing yourself.

285
00:20:37,980 --> 00:20:41,040
Director Park Min Jun!

286
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:43,350
Please...

287
00:20:43,950 --> 00:20:45,950
Please, just go.

288
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:50,990
I'll handle my situation myself,

289
00:20:51,490 --> 00:20:53,260
so stop meddling in my business.

290
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:11,940
This shouldn't be happening.

291
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:16,550
Why is Park Min Jun with Chloe?

292
00:21:20,150 --> 00:21:22,490
You were just doing as Chloe said?

293
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:23,820
That's right.

294
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:29,490
Chloe's the real problem.
She'll make more trouble for you.

295
00:21:29,730 --> 00:21:32,130
Killing me here
won't solve anything.

296
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,730
Please, let me see the chairman.

297
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:39,200
If I tell the chairman
everything Chloe is plotting,

298
00:21:40,100 --> 00:21:42,470
it could benefit you too, ma'am.

299
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:47,840
If we work together, we both win.

300
00:21:58,990 --> 00:22:02,630
What is this?
Some kind of sick joke?

301
00:22:03,460 --> 00:22:06,930
Calm down and hear Ms. Choi out.

302
00:22:07,060 --> 00:22:08,800
I'm telling you,
she has crucial information.

303
00:22:08,870 --> 00:22:10,400
Crucial information? As if.

304
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,800
You must've fallen for her lies...

305
00:22:13,070 --> 00:22:15,170
and messed everything up.

306
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:17,170
No, that's not it at all.

307
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:23,850
I was wrong, sir.

308
00:22:25,780 --> 00:22:29,590
You must've come to your senses
after your brush with death,

309
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:31,050
but it's too late.

310
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:33,860
Even if you make it
out of here alive,

311
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:37,760
you'll pay for deceiving
and blackmailing me, Park Tae Ho...

312
00:22:37,760 --> 00:22:39,060
It was because of Chloe.

313
00:22:41,260 --> 00:22:43,130
What? Chloe?

314
00:22:43,970 --> 00:22:47,940
I only deceived and blackmailed you
because of Chloe.

315
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:51,910
She put me up to it and used me.
I was deceived too.

316
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:56,780
She used you to sabotage me?

317
00:22:58,250 --> 00:23:00,980
Why? What's her motive?

318
00:23:02,850 --> 00:23:07,190
She's after the bio division.
That's why she came to Adele.

319
00:23:08,530 --> 00:23:11,860
See? I told you she knew something.

320
00:23:13,300 --> 00:23:15,770
I knew that sly fox was
up to something.

321
00:23:15,830 --> 00:23:18,970
She tried to seduce Hyun Jun
and use him.

322
00:23:20,070 --> 00:23:22,070
She's after the bio division?

323
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:26,280
Explain in detail.

324
00:23:27,140 --> 00:23:29,510
Well, the recording...

325
00:23:34,180 --> 00:23:37,590
She approached me
when I returned after being fired.

326
00:23:38,320 --> 00:23:40,760
She asked whether I had
any leverage against you.

327
00:23:40,760 --> 00:23:42,990
Then she told me to help her
acquire the bio division...

328
00:23:42,990 --> 00:23:44,030
for next to nothing.

329
00:23:44,090 --> 00:23:47,300
After that,
she insisted I had to blackmail you,

330
00:23:48,430 --> 00:23:51,540
that I had to fight you for it.

331
00:23:52,300 --> 00:23:54,810
I'm also a victim of Chloe.

332
00:23:55,170 --> 00:23:56,270
Chloe?

333
00:23:57,710 --> 00:23:59,210
So, Chloe...

334
00:24:03,050 --> 00:24:04,380
Let me prove it to you.

335
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:08,390
Let me prove that Chloe is
after the bio division and could be...

336
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:10,720
a threat to you.

337
00:24:15,830 --> 00:24:19,530
You want Ms. Oh's son,
Director Park Hyun Jun,

338
00:24:20,060 --> 00:24:21,900
removed from his position?

339
00:24:23,100 --> 00:24:27,740
I see you're finally making
your move in the succession race.

340
00:24:29,970 --> 00:24:31,210
Are you disappointed...

341
00:24:32,340 --> 00:24:33,610
that my fight...

342
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:36,010
with Chairman Park Tae Ho
and Ms. Oh Jung Ran...

343
00:24:36,350 --> 00:24:37,780
has become a succession battle?

344
00:24:38,320 --> 00:24:39,650
Not at all.

345
00:24:40,650 --> 00:24:44,120
It's a necessary step
if you're going to fight those two.

346
00:24:44,490 --> 00:24:48,120
I took that into account
when I offered to help you.

347
00:24:49,490 --> 00:24:50,490
So,

348
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:53,700
how can I be of assistance?

349
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:57,600
As you know,
I'm not in a position...

350
00:24:57,900 --> 00:25:01,710
to demand Director Park Hyun Jun's
dismissal myself.

351
00:25:02,540 --> 00:25:05,540
I need someone to be my voice.

352
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:08,350
Someone with enough clout...

353
00:25:08,910 --> 00:25:11,250
to pressure Chairman Park Tae Ho?

354
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:15,650
Yes. That's why I want to meet...

355
00:25:15,950 --> 00:25:19,520
Adele's largest
individual shareholder.

356
00:25:19,820 --> 00:25:22,330
His name is Moon Tae Jin.

357
00:25:33,900 --> 00:25:35,540
What are your thoughts on this?

358
00:25:36,610 --> 00:25:40,810
My father and even my mother.
Are they really that kind of people?

359
00:25:42,150 --> 00:25:43,610
If that's true,

360
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:46,480
then what does that make me?

361
00:25:55,790 --> 00:25:58,060
I kept telling myself
the truth didn't matter,

362
00:25:59,530 --> 00:26:02,100
and that regardless of
what my father had done,

363
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:03,500
I'd insist I was innocent.

364
00:26:05,040 --> 00:26:06,470
But now that things
have come to this,

365
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:10,210
how can I face Park Min Jun
and Baek Jin Ju...

366
00:26:11,610 --> 00:26:13,310
as if I've done nothing wrong?

367
00:26:15,710 --> 00:26:16,910
Hyun Jun.

368
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:22,420
Hyun Jun.

369
00:26:24,520 --> 00:26:26,190
- What is it?
- Well...

370
00:26:27,090 --> 00:26:30,230
I was worried about a few things.

371
00:26:30,930 --> 00:26:32,830
If this is about Ms. Oh,
then forget it.

372
00:26:33,430 --> 00:26:34,430
Please leave.

373
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:39,400
Is that for Chloe?

374
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:42,270
Good. If you're planning to propose,
do it quickly...

375
00:26:42,540 --> 00:26:44,110
before Park Min Jun gets involved.

376
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:48,310
Why are you bringing Min Jun
into this?

377
00:26:52,150 --> 00:26:53,150
What is it?

378
00:26:53,320 --> 00:26:55,490
- Did something happen?
- What?

379
00:26:56,250 --> 00:26:57,690
It's just that...

380
00:26:59,190 --> 00:27:02,030
For certain reasons,
I was keeping watch,

381
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:05,260
and I saw him follow her
out of the hospital room...

382
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:07,660
Her hospital room?

383
00:27:07,730 --> 00:27:11,940
Yes, it seems he heard Chloe
was hospitalized and came to visit.

384
00:27:13,040 --> 00:27:15,070
Chloe's in the hospital? Why?

385
00:27:15,910 --> 00:27:16,910
Wait a minute.

386
00:27:17,410 --> 00:27:18,740
You didn't know?

387
00:27:22,350 --> 00:27:23,350
Which hospital?

388
00:27:23,580 --> 00:27:27,320
The general hospital
near the Adele warehouse... Hey!

389
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:28,690
Hyun Jun!

390
00:27:34,490 --> 00:27:35,490
Hold on.

391
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:38,260
Hyun Jun didn't even know...

392
00:27:38,730 --> 00:27:42,130
Chloe was in the hospital,
but Park Min Jun went to visit her?

393
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:47,240
Don't tell me Chloe was the one
who called him.

394
00:27:48,610 --> 00:27:50,570
Instead of calling Hyun Jun,

395
00:27:51,810 --> 00:27:53,340
she only called Park Min Jun?

396
00:27:55,210 --> 00:27:56,210
This could mean...

397
00:27:56,950 --> 00:27:59,080
Park Min Jun isn't the only one
with feelings.

398
00:28:00,250 --> 00:28:02,050
Chloe might feel the same way.

399
00:28:03,450 --> 00:28:04,820
What are you talking about?

400
00:28:07,890 --> 00:28:09,790
I heard everything
on my way up here.

401
00:28:10,730 --> 00:28:13,260
I had you watching
Chloe's hospital room,

402
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:15,900
and Park Min Jun showed up there?

403
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:19,840
Does he have feelings for Chloe?

404
00:28:20,670 --> 00:28:23,740
I don't know. I don't know anything.

405
00:28:31,010 --> 00:28:34,080
Park Min Jun likes Chloe?

406
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:38,250
It's... No, it's just
a one-sided crush.

407
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:41,620
There's nothing going on
between Hyun Jun and Chloe,

408
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:44,530
so don't use this as an excuse
to object to their marriage.

409
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:47,030
Of course.

410
00:28:47,730 --> 00:28:49,530
Something felt off back then too.

411
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:54,570
Don't you ever
treat Chloe like that again.

412
00:28:56,170 --> 00:28:57,240
Is this the kind of man you are?

413
00:28:57,510 --> 00:28:59,680
How could you let Chloe
be treated this way?

414
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,540
That's right.

415
00:29:02,710 --> 00:29:05,120
So that's what that look
in his eyes meant.

416
00:29:07,650 --> 00:29:09,450
Park Min Jun and Chloe.

417
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:14,060
Well, now.
This is getting interesting.

418
00:29:19,700 --> 00:29:22,030
Where could Choi Yu Na be?

419
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:31,440
When did you wake up?

420
00:29:34,010 --> 00:29:35,010
A little while ago.

421
00:29:35,310 --> 00:29:37,580
Where have you been at this hour?

422
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:40,550
I was just...

423
00:29:43,520 --> 00:29:44,820
I was scared, so I hid.

424
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:47,560
You were scared?

425
00:29:48,930 --> 00:29:49,930
Today's accident...

426
00:29:50,390 --> 00:29:52,200
was Chairman Park trying to kill me.

427
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:55,270
I was terrified
the moment I woke up,

428
00:29:55,730 --> 00:29:56,930
and I couldn't stay in my room.

429
00:29:57,600 --> 00:30:00,040
Chairman Park could've sent someone
after me again.

430
00:30:01,340 --> 00:30:02,540
I see you understand the situation.

431
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:05,410
Things could've gone badly
if I hadn't been there.

432
00:30:08,710 --> 00:30:10,380
Are you expecting a "thank you?"

433
00:30:11,750 --> 00:30:15,120
I want to hear
what your plan is now.

434
00:30:17,020 --> 00:30:18,620
I'm going to get through
this crisis...

435
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:20,920
even if it means using you.

436
00:30:24,790 --> 00:30:27,160
I refuse to die
at Chairman Park's hands,

437
00:30:28,460 --> 00:30:29,800
so I'll do whatever it takes.

438
00:30:32,100 --> 00:30:33,100
Whatever it takes?

439
00:30:34,700 --> 00:30:35,710
Then...

440
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:41,880
does that mean
you'd kill Park Tae Ho?

441
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:49,090
Are you being serious?

442
00:30:49,790 --> 00:30:51,490
We're talking about a human life.

443
00:30:52,090 --> 00:30:53,760
This isn't something I'd joke about.

444
00:30:54,760 --> 00:30:56,030
Chairman Park...

445
00:30:56,460 --> 00:30:58,930
will stop at nothing
until you're dead.

446
00:31:00,860 --> 00:31:04,670
The only way for you to survive
is to eliminate Park Tae Ho.

447
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:07,400
If you're willing to go
that far to survive,

448
00:31:08,300 --> 00:31:09,440
I'll help you.

449
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:14,040
You'd do...

450
00:31:15,210 --> 00:31:17,110
something that risky for my sake?

451
00:31:18,780 --> 00:31:20,450
It's for my own good too.

452
00:31:21,350 --> 00:31:22,550
With Chairman Park
out of the picture,

453
00:31:22,850 --> 00:31:25,390
it'll be much easier for me
to take over the bio division.

454
00:31:27,790 --> 00:31:30,490
So, can you make up your mind now?

455
00:31:36,530 --> 00:31:39,470
Yes. My mind's made up.

456
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:42,310
Even if killing someone is
what it takes,

457
00:31:44,370 --> 00:31:45,580
I'll survive.

458
00:31:48,540 --> 00:31:49,550
Good.

459
00:31:50,180 --> 00:31:53,080
Then I'll find
the right time and place...

460
00:31:53,550 --> 00:31:56,420
to make our move on Chairman Park.

461
00:32:10,970 --> 00:32:11,970
How dare she...

462
00:32:13,070 --> 00:32:14,800
go after Adele's bio division...

463
00:32:16,370 --> 00:32:18,070
and come after me too?

464
00:32:42,230 --> 00:32:45,300
(Pearl in Red)

465
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:47,640
Park Tae Ho will never leave me.

466
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:49,270
There are things only I can do.

467
00:32:49,340 --> 00:32:51,910
Just you wait.
I'm going to show you...

468
00:32:51,970 --> 00:32:53,940
exactly what it is
that only I can do.

469
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:57,280
Get your murderous hands off me.

470
00:32:57,510 --> 00:33:00,250
You don't have a son anymore.

471
00:33:00,550 --> 00:33:04,290
Tonight, lure Chloe
to the Adele warehouse.

472
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:06,460
I have no choice
but to do as she says.

473
00:33:07,220 --> 00:33:08,790
I'm just luring her there.

474
00:33:09,630 --> 00:33:10,890
That's all I have to do.

475
00:33:11,530 --> 00:33:13,530
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
